？？？: Waaaa!!!
Jasmine: Don't tell me... did someone get attacked by "Desert Black King"?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Did bad buggy attack again?
Young Master Bear: H... Help...
Handsome Bear: Waahhh! Don't burn my hair!
Dumb Bear Soldier: What a big bad buggy!
Jasmine: That's not bug. That's the notorious desert lizard...
Dumb Bear Soldier: Bad Buggy! No bullying Jasmine!
Dumb Bear Soldier: I think... I won? ......
Young Master Bear: Sister, you alright?
Jasmine: Who's your sister! Why are you guys here?
Young Master Bear: After I marry Miss Rose, you'll become my sister. Therefore, it's also natural I'm the one to protect you.
Dumb Bear Soldier: Wow, you're getting married. Congratulations~~
Jasmine: That's totally NOT the case!
Handsome Bear: That's right. No matter how you look at it, I'm the more handsome one. Miss Rose will definitely choose me.
Dumb Bear Soldier: Congratulations to you both~~
Jasmine: Big Dumb Bear, stop believing every single stuff people say! Rose would never ever marry these two!
Young Master Bear: Sigh, regular females have such bad tempers. They simply not as perfect as Miss Rose. She never gets angry.
Jasmine: And how did you know that Rose never gets angry? Let me tell you; she not only gets angry, but she also hits people.
Handsome Bear: Sister, lying is bad~ Miss Rose is such beauty. She would never throw temper tantrums.
Young Master Bear: Yikes~ I'm starving from all this talking...
Young Master Bear: Eh? There's a lunch box sitting there!
Jasmine: Don't touch that!
Young Master Bear: Ewww... Who's going to eat such gross boxed lunch!
Handsome Bear: Such an unappealing boxed lunch does not match my aesthetics. You can save it for yourselves.
Young Master Bear: Sister, we shall go and search the surroundings for any potential dangers~
Jasmine: The food is all mushed up from the shaking. But...
Jasmine: Everyone just gave up without even having a bite. Why do they just care about the outside and not at all about the inside?
Dumb Bear Soldier: So much food~ Yippee~ So happy~~
Jasmine: You... don't you think this boxed lunch is ugly?
Dumb Bear Soldier: So can't eat food if they are ugly?
Jasmine: That's not really the point either...
Dumb Bear Soldier: Tasty lunch box always tasty no matter how they look~
Dumb Bear Soldier: Ah! ......
Jasmine: What's wrong?
Dumb Bear Soldier: I forgot to save some for you. I've eaten almost whole thing...
Jasmine: .........
Jasmine: It's alright; I'm not hungry. If you like it, you can eat all of it.
Dumb Bear Soldier: Yeah~~ Then I will dig in!
Dumb Bear Soldier: Ah~ nom nom nom~~
